  "description": "This individual is an undead human of spare, desiccated build, with light skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a long, angular jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets beneath a heavy brow ridge, giving the face a fixed, unblinking severity. White hair grows in thin, uneven strands, worn long and habitually gathered back from the face by ingrained habit rather than comfort. The hands and neck show pronounced corded tendons and darkened, leathery patches consistent with long decay rather than recent injury.",
